Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族会找你算账的！\N{\fs40}House Velaryon is coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:26.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,海蛇会砍下你那该死的麻脸脑袋！\N{\fs40}The Sea Snake will have your poxy fucking head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:28.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不……不要啊！\N{\fs40}No... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,求你了！不！\N{\fs40}No! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:38.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去死吧 达哈尔亲王\N{\fs40}Fuck you, Prince Drahar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:43.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,日你婊子老母！日你杂种老爹！\N{\fs40}Fuck your whore mother and bastard father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,操！\N{\fs40}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:46.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要啊！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:48.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙王子万岁！\N{\fs40}Hail, Prince Daemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:23.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,烧死这帮天杀的三城同盟会杂种！\N{\fs40}Burn the fucking Triarchy cunts alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子 我在这里！\N{\fs40}Here, my prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,救我！\N{\fs40}Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:44.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 直接回洞里去！  - 快回洞里！快！\N{\fs40}- Direct to the caves! - To the caves! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:48.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,撤退！撤到洞里面！\N{\fs40}Retreat! Retreat to the caves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,快回洞里！\N{\fs40}Back to the caves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在哪？\N{\fs40}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出来面对我 达哈尔！\N{\fs40}Come out and face me, Drahar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,快滚出来 达哈尔！\N{\fs40}Come out, Drahar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人躲哪里去了？\N{\fs40}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要把你喂给你自己的螃蟹！\N{\fs40}I'm gonna feed you to your own crabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你人呢？\N{\fs40}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的头发像您 陛下\N{\fs40}He has your hair, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:19.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他的头发确实像我 - 他的眼睛也像您 陛下\N{\fs40}- He does have my hair. - He has your eyes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说得没错\N{\fs40}Yes, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的鼻子也很像我 是不是呀？\N{\fs40}And you have my nose, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:27.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,刚刚两岁 这孩子就已经生得一副帝王相了\N{\fs40}Two years old and already our boy has a kingly presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许吧 哥哥 不过今天早晨\N{\fs40}He may yet, brother but this morning he insisted
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他非要用手喝粥\N{\fs40}on eating porridge with his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会长大的\N{\fs40}He will grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都是因为他 这么多人聚集于此\N{\fs40}We've quite a party assembled in his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:45.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然这次狩猎结束后 我们就有更多值得庆祝的事了\N{\fs40}And surely by the end of this hunt, we shall have more to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:47.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您说 有什么值得庆祝的事呢？\N{\fs40}And what is that, pray tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:51.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是伊耿的第二个命名日 他已经不再是小婴儿了\N{\fs40}It is Aegon's second name day. His infancy's behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就等韦赛里斯指定他为铁王座的继承人了\N{\fs40}It only remains for Viserys to name him heir to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:56.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可没这么确定\N{\fs40}I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是国王的长子\N{\fs40}He's the king's firstborn son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:00.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得陛下还没有认清这件事\N{\fs40}I don't know that His Grace sees it so clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:05.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就靠你来让他看清了……\N{\fs40}Then it lies with you to make him see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首相大人\N{\fs40}Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从石阶列岛带来了急报\N{\fs40}I bring urgent news from the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,螃蟹喂食者被围困在血石岛后躲了起来\N{\fs40}The Crabfeeder has dug in for siege on Bloodstone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,同时他的部下趁着夜色摧毁我们的舰队\N{\fs40}while his men sabotage our fleet under cover of dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,泰兰 今天别提这个\N{\fs40}Not today, Tyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只怕石阶列岛的事情万分火急\N{\fs40}The matter at the Stepstones is regrettably urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:27.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经开战三年了 再等三天也无妨\N{\fs40}It's been three years. It can wait another three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:33.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来吧……吃点东西\N{\fs40}Come... eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,弥补赶路的辛苦\N{\fs40}Fortify yourselves for the journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别客气\N{\fs40}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,补给车队准备好了吗？\N{\fs40}Is the baggage train ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在正在临河门集结\N{\fs40}It is presently massing at the River Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰森公爵希望我们中午前抵达御林\N{\fs40}Lord Jason expects us in the Kingswood before midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:49.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你看见雷妮拉了吗？ - 没看到 陛下\N{\fs40}- Have you seen Rhaenyra? - I have not, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,三城同盟会的人躲进血石岛的洞穴\N{\fs40}With the Triarchy now sheltering in Bloodstone's caves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙的威胁大大降低了\N{\fs40}the threat of the dragons is blunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们没有步兵吗？\N{\fs40}They don't have foot soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:02.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们的雇佣兵已经陆续撤离了 陛下\N{\fs40}But their sellswords have been withdrawing in droves, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就连他们也看得出这是场必败的战斗\N{\fs40}Even the mercenaries can see that it is a losing effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉在哪里？\N{\fs40}Where's Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也不确定 陛下\N{\fs40}I cannot be sure at present, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族的军队消耗很严重 陛下\N{\fs40}The Velaryon forces have suffered heavy attrition, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,士兵之间已经怨声载道了\N{\fs40}The seeds of dissent are sown amongst the rank and file.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙用兵太严苛\N{\fs40}Daemon has driven the men hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,士兵们开始质疑他的命令了\N{\fs40}They have begun to question his command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果国王打算干预此事的话……\N{\fs40}If the crown were ever to intervene...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.03,0:07:26.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 泰兰 - 现在是时候了\N{\fs40}- Tyland. - now is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙和海蛇未经陛下准许就擅自开战\N{\fs40}Daemon and the Sea Snake started their war without His Grace's leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都过了这么久 如果国王现在干预\N{\fs40}Were he to intervene now, after so long
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会让我们显得软弱\N{\fs40}it would make the crown appear weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七层地狱啊 谁能告诉我\N{\fs40}Can someone tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉到底在哪？\N{\fs40}where in the Seven Hells Rhaenyra might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:45.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在巨龙眼皮底下\N{\fs40}Under the dragon's eye
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:51.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在巨龙眼皮底下\N{\fs40}Under the dragon's eye
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再来一遍\N{\fs40}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许公主想听些别的歌谣？\N{\fs40}Perhaps the Princess might like to hear something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不想 再唱一遍\N{\fs40}She would not. Play it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:10.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她带着舰队和子民逃离\N{\fs40}She fled with her ships And her people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:13.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,心碎只为那……\N{\fs40}Her heart broken for those...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:17.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我说停了吗？\N{\fs40}Did I say to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从头再来\N{\fs40}From the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:33.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她带着舰队\N{\fs40}She fled with her ships
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 和子民逃离 - 雷妮拉？\N{\fs40}- And her people - Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:36.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么了 王后陛下？\N{\fs40}Yes, my Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家都在外庭等你呢\N{\fs40}Your presence is wanted in the outer courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王室狩猎马上要出发了\N{\fs40}The royal hunt readies to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:44.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我决定还是留在这读书\N{\fs40}I have decided to remain here and read instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你可以走了 山姆威尔\N{\fs40}You may go, Samwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主命令你留下来\N{\fs40}You are to stay by order of the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后命令你立刻离开神木林\N{\fs40}The Queen commands you to leave the Godswood at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,告辞了 公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:07.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王希望你可以加入我们\N{\fs40}The King wishes for you to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王有很多值得庆祝的事 用不着我去\N{\fs40}The King has much to celebrate. He does not need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:13.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他想要我们一起去\N{\fs40}He wants for us all to be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许狩猎会很有趣\N{\fs40}Perhaps the hunt could be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是国王的命令吗？\N{\fs40}Is it the King's command?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:22.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是 不过…… - 那现在就走 王后陛下\N{\fs40}- Yes, but it... - Then at once, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也不用这样的\N{\fs40}But it needn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说真的 我们大可不必如此 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}None of it needs be this way, in truth, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看 这样不是挺好吗？\N{\fs40}Well, isn't this splendid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们全家外出庆祝\N{\fs40}The whole of our family off to celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并在御林中探险\N{\fs40}and adventure in the Kingswood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你现在这样适合外出吗？\N{\fs40}Should you be traveling in such condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:56.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,学士们说出来亲近大自然会有好处\N{\fs40}The maesters said that being out in nature would do me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:59.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迟早你也会有你自己的孩子\N{\fs40}You'll be with your own child, sooner than late
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:01.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让我成为一个骄傲的外公\N{\fs40}and make me a proud grandsire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也没那么糟糕\N{\fs40}It's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怀孕是有点久 不过伊耿出生得很快\N{\fs40}The days are long but Aegon came quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也没遇到什么麻烦\N{\fs40}and without fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天你应该和我一同骑马外出\N{\fs40}You should ride out with me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,参加围猎\N{\fs40}Join in the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想\N{\fs40}I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,野猪在被猎杀的时候叫得像小孩子一样\N{\fs40}The boars squeal like children when they're being slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不怎么喜欢\N{\fs40}I find it discomforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:31.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这只是狩猎 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}It's a hunt, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:37.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想怎么参与?\N{\fs40}How would you like to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我也不知道为什么叫我去\N{\fs40}I'm not sure why I'm asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为你是我女儿 是公主\N{\fs40}Because you are my daughter. The Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以你肩负责任\N{\fs40}And you have duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以我时刻被提醒这些\N{\fs40}As I am ceaselessly reminded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 什么？ - 所以我时刻都被提醒这些\N{\fs40}- I'm sorry? - As I am ceaselessly reminded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:52.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你积极参与的话就不需要提醒了\N{\fs40}You wouldn't need to be reminded if you ever attended to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:54.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没人是为我而来的\N{\fs40}No one's here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁\N{\fs40}Hail, hail, Aegon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:59.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征服者伊耿宝宝 二世！\N{\fs40}the Conqueror-Babe, Second of His Name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:03.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是说殿下的第二个命名日！\N{\fs40}Here's to His Grace on his second name day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有消息说乔汉娜小姐被拐走了\N{\fs40}Lady Johanna was reported to have been abducted
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:55.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就在史文大人的船经过石阶列岛的时候\N{\fs40}when one of Lord Swann's ships sailed through the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那乔汉娜小姐会怎么样？\N{\fs40}What will happen to Lady Johanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:00.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她会被卖到自由城邦的青楼里\N{\fs40}She's to be sold to a pillow house in the Free Cities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果谣言是真的话\N{\fs40}if you believe the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恐怕众神没把我造得适合狩猎\N{\fs40}I fear the gods did not make me for hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:10.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我能与你们同坐吗 夫人们？  - 当然 一起坐吧\N{\fs40}- Might I sit with you, my ladies? - Of course, please join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:14.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这位是拉里斯·斯壮 我们法务大臣莱昂诺的小儿子\N{\fs40}Larys Strong, the youngest son of our master of laws, Lord Lyonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:16.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我夫君说还没有国王能\N{\fs40}My lord husband says that no king has ever been able
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,长久地驯服石阶列岛\N{\fs40}to tame the Stepstones for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:21.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就是一片不毛之地 只适合野蛮人\N{\fs40}It's an inhospitable place, suited only for savages.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:25.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许公主殿下可以给我们讲讲\N{\fs40}Perhaps the Princess can give us some insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:30.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 我不知道怎么说 我从没去过石阶列岛\N{\fs40}Oh, I'm not sure how I could. I've never been to the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:34.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你亲爱的叔叔是这场战争背后的主使 是吗？\N{\fs40}Your dear uncle is the great mind behind this war, is he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我已经很多年没跟戴蒙说过话了\N{\fs40}I wouldn't know. I have not spoken to Daemon in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从你取代他成为王位继承人之后吧\N{\fs40}Since you supplanted him as heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙自己做出的选择 凯拉夫人\N{\fs40}Daemon made his choices, Lady Ceira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主更适合成为继承人\N{\fs40}The Princess was more suited to the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他弄得一团糟 国王必须出面解决\N{\fs40}He's made a mess and the King must put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:51.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,派出舰队和士兵 把三城同盟会清理干净\N{\fs40}Send fleets and men, and clear out the Triarchy for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是国王没有参战\N{\fs40}But the crown is not at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国已经参战了 公主\N{\fs40}The crown is at war, Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然你父亲不肯承认\N{\fs40}though your father refuses to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们已经被你叔叔和海蛇拖进战争了\N{\fs40}We've been dragged into it by your uncle and the Sea Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么您又是如何报效王国的呢 雷德温夫人？\N{\fs40}And how have you served the realm of late, Lady Redwyne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,吃蛋糕吗？\N{\fs40}By eating cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很好奇 公主\N{\fs40}I wonder, Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.18,0:14:45.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的第二个命名日也有这么气派吗？\N{\fs40}was your own second name day as grand as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说实话我一点也不记得了 伊耿也不会记得\N{\fs40}I honestly don't recall and neither will Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:52.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是杰森·兰尼斯特公爵\N{\fs40}Lord Jason Lannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看到这么多狮子就猜到了\N{\fs40}I gathered that from all the lions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们应该没有正式见过\N{\fs40}I don't think we've been properly introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:03.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的双胞胎弟弟是我父亲的御前会议成员\N{\fs40}Your twin serves on my father's council.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,泰兰这个人...\N{\fs40}Tyland is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:10.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,十分迟钝 诸神保佑他\N{\fs40}frightfully dull, Gods love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这会是你尝过的最好的蜜酒\N{\fs40}The finest honeyed wine you'll ever taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 当然 是兰尼斯港产的  - 当然\N{\fs40}- Made in Lannisport, of course. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:19.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御林 真是个好猎场\N{\fs40}The Kingswood, it's a fine hunting ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:23.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是最好的地方在凯岩城 我家附近\N{\fs40}But the best spot is to be found at Casterly Rock, near my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你去过吗？\N{\fs40}Have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:29.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,旅行时去过一次 小时候和我母亲一起\N{\fs40}Once. On tour, with my mother when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说实话我也不怎么记得了\N{\fs40}And honestly can't recall much of that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,凯岩城的高度是旧镇参天塔的三倍\N{\fs40}The Rock is thrice the height of the Hightower in Oldtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至比北境的绝境长城还高\N{\fs40}Taller still than the Wall in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:40.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据说如果天气足够好的话\N{\fs40}It's been said that if one were to stand in the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,站在塔顶能清楚地看到日落之海对岸\N{\fs40}on a perfect day, one could see clear across the Sunset Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那肯定很壮观\N{\fs40}It must be quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:49.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 我们没有龙穴 不过...\N{\fs40}We don't have a Dragonpit, of course, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:52.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有办法和资源能够建造一个\N{\fs40}I do have the means and resources to build one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你为什么要建龙穴？\N{\fs40}Why would you need a Dragonpit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:58.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然是为了给龙安家\N{\fs40}To house dragons, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会为了我的女王做任何事\N{\fs40}I'd do anything for my Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者...为了夫人\N{\fs40}or... lady wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:11.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,感谢你的酒\N{\fs40}Thank you for the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这就是我对于你的价值？\N{\fs40}Is that what I am to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给大贵族的奖赏？\N{\fs40}A prize to proffer about to the great houses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你到年龄了 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}You're of age, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:40.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰森·兰尼斯特是位佳偶\N{\fs40}Jason Lannister is an excellent match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他傲慢又自我\N{\fs40}He's arrogant and self-serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:44.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我以为你们在这方面倒是挺像\N{\fs40}Well, I thought you might have that in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从你成年以来\N{\fs40}Since you came of age
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全国各地的来信像河流汇集成湖\N{\fs40}I've been slowly drowning in a lake of parchment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,慢慢地快把我淹死了\N{\fs40}flowing from every corner of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全是在提亲\N{\fs40}Marriage proposals, all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且我多次试着跟你讨论这件事\N{\fs40}And I have tried, often, to discuss it with you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可你每次都拒绝我\N{\fs40}but you've refused me at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是因为我不想结婚\N{\fs40}That is because I do not wish to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,连我都必须屈服于传统和职责 雷妮拉！\N{\fs40}Even I do not exist above tradition and duty, Rhaenyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:04.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,打扰了 陛下\N{\fs40}Excuse me, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你必须嫁人\N{\fs40}You must marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:18.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 什么事？ - 王家猎手有消息\N{\fs40}- Yes? - The royal huntsman
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,需要汇报 陛下\N{\fs40}has sent a report, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:23.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有人目击到一头白色的雄鹿\N{\fs40}There's been a sighting of a white hart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:26.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那头鹿是御林之王 陛下\N{\fs40}The stag is the king of the Kingswood, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个献给伊耿王子命名日的帝王之兆\N{\fs40}A regal portent for Prince Aegon's name day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fs40}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 等等！\N{\fs40}Princess, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 慢下来！\N{\fs40}Princess, slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:33.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主！\N{\fs40}Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出什么事了？\N{\fs40}What happened back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:54.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的父亲\N{\fs40}My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:57.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想把我卖给杰森·兰尼斯特\N{\fs40}Trying to sell me off to Jason Lannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:01.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是...\N{\fs40}Was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:04.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是不是我被册封为铁王座的继承人\N{\fs40}was I named heir to the Iron Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只是为了用我来进一步提升\N{\fs40}so that I might only further raise the standing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:08.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,凯岩城公爵的地位？\N{\fs40}of a lord of Casterly Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您想让我杀了他吗？\N{\fs40}You want me to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们应该返回营地 公主\N{\fs40}We should return to camp, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天天气不错\N{\fs40}It's a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们应该逛逛御林\N{\fs40}We should take in the Kingswood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:38.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你订过婚吗 克里斯顿爵士？\N{\fs40}Were you ever betrothed, Ser Criston?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我当然也曾是个热衷冒险的青年\N{\fs40}I had an adventurous youth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那时我父亲在黑港侍奉\N{\fs40}when my father served at Blackhaven, to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是我的地位还够不上一门正式的婚约\N{\fs40}But my station was never high enough for a formal betrothal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我宣誓成为御林铁卫之前\N{\fs40}Before I spoke my vows as a knight of the Kingsguard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我想的话 可能会娶一个平民女孩\N{\fs40}I could have married a common-born girl had I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你能为自己的人生做主 真幸运\N{\fs40}How lucky you are to have a say in your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国里很多人愿意您交换位置 公主\N{\fs40}Many in the realm would gladly trade positions with you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那只是因为他们不在我这个位置罢了\N{\fs40}Only because none of them has ever held my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:07.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我虽然是龙石岛的公主 但却没有实权\N{\fs40}I may be the Princess of Dragonstone, but I am toothless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从前\N{\fs40}One day
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:13.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没几年前\N{\fs40}not so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是您的权力把我的名字写进了白典\N{\fs40}you held enough power to write my name into the White Book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让您父亲册封我为御林铁卫\N{\fs40}When your father named me to his Kingsguard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是科尔家族从未有过的最高荣誉\N{\fs40}it was the highest honor any Cole had ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:25.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我所拥有的一切都是您给的\N{\fs40}All that I have, I owe to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以我可不认为您没有实权 公主\N{\fs40}Now I'd hardly call that toothless, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 陛下  - 还有多远?\N{\fs40}- Your Grace. - How far?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们在东边半里格的地方发现它的粪便\N{\fs40}The droppings were found half a league to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:15.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 还是新鲜的  - 是两三小时前的 陛下\N{\fs40}- Still fresh. - Between two and three hours, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:17.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我最好的探子看到它了\N{\fs40}My best scout spied him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:21.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这野兽重达35石 现在我们已经找到了它的踪迹\N{\fs40}The beast is upward of 35 stone, and we now have his trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 是啊 - 在巨龙统治维斯特洛之前\N{\fs40}- Aye. - Before the dragons ruled over Westeros
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,白鹿才是这片土地上王室的象征\N{\fs40}the white hart was the symbol of royalty in these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且偏偏是在今天……\N{\fs40}And on this day, of all days...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从不迷信预兆 陛下\N{\fs40}I've never been one for signs and portents, Your Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果诸神真的愿意表示眷顾……\N{\fs40}but if the gods did wish to show their favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:27.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是我家黄金长廊\N{\fs40}I had this forged in the Golden Gallery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:28.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为伊耿王子打造的\N{\fs40}in honor of Prince Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:42.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真是个好东西\N{\fs40}It's quite a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望能用它给白鹿\N{\fs40}I hope it might provide the killing stroke
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.66,0:22:47.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,刺出致命一击\N{\fs40}against your white hart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御林之王\N{\fs40}King of the Kingswood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好像七神也祝福了这一天\N{\fs40}It's as if the Seven themselves have blessed this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,感谢你的慷慨\N{\fs40}Thank you for your generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:04.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果能娶雷妮拉公主为妻\N{\fs40}I would be honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:07.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将十分荣幸\N{\fs40}to take the Princess Rhaenyra to wife
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:11.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能为您\N{\fs40}What I offer you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:14.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为王室和您女儿提供力量\N{\fs40}the crown and your daughter, is strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:21.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你觉得坦格利安家族还需要力量吗?\N{\fs40}Do you think that House Targaryen wants for strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果有人能够给您更多龙 您不要吗?\N{\fs40}If someone offered you more dragons, would you not take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:27.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你能给我龙吗?\N{\fs40}Do you have dragons to offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:32.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,凯岩城是个富丽堂皇的地方\N{\fs40}Casterly Rock is a splendid seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:36.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉坐在我身边不会丢脸\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra may take her place there by my side without shame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:39.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也能很好地弥补她身份地位的损失\N{\fs40}and feel herself well-compensated for her loss in station.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:41.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她的身份地位有什么损失?\N{\fs40}What loss of station?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:46.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果您要册封小伊耿为继承人 陛下\N{\fs40}If you were to name young Aegon heir, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.39,0:23:48.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我什么时候说要这样做了?\N{\fs40}And when would I be doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.81,0:23:51.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是以为……\N{\fs40}I had assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毕竟他是您的长子 我们很多人都认为……\N{\fs40}As he is your firstborn son, many of us had assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:56.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说“我们很多人”\N{\fs40}"Many of us," you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:24:00.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的封臣质疑我对继承人的选择了吗?\N{\fs40}Have your bannermen questioned my choice of heir?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-  当然没有 陛下  - 如果有此等叛乱\N{\fs40}- Of course not, Your Grace. - It is your sworn duty
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:05.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你有责任上报给我\N{\fs40}to report rebellion stirring in my kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.20,0:24:08.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,叛乱? 没有这种事 陛下\N{\fs40}Rebellion? There has been nothing of the sort, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-  我只是……  - 我不是一时兴起\N{\fs40}- I was only... - I did not decide to name Rhaenyra
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,才决定册封雷妮拉为继承人\N{\fs40}my heir on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.04,0:24:17.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国里所有领主都最好牢记这点\N{\fs40}All the lords of the kingdom would do well to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:23.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,感谢你的礼物\N{\fs40}Thank you for the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:27.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:33.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上酒\N{\fs40}Wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.65,0:24:48.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,猎人发现踪迹了 陛下\N{\fs40}The huntsman has the trail, Your Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.57,0:24:50.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经派出了猎犬\N{\fs40}and has sent out the hounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.16,0:24:52.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,白鹿很快就会被逼入绝境了\N{\fs40}It won't be long now until the white hart is cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:54.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的猎物唾手可得\N{\fs40}Your prize is within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.33,0:24:59.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您怎么看杰森大人的求婚?\N{\fs40}What do you make of Lord Jason's proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:03.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他真不是一般的傲慢\N{\fs40}That man's pride has pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.84,0:25:09.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您不只是雷妮拉的父亲 您是国王\N{\fs40}You're not only Rhaenyra's father, you're the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.18,0:25:12.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她会按照你的命令做的\N{\fs40}She will do as you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.27,0:25:16.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我并不想命令她 奥托\N{\fs40}It is not my wish to command her, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.81,0:25:19.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只想让她快乐\N{\fs40}I want her to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.65,0:25:28.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,凯岩城之外还有一个选择\N{\fs40}There is another choice, beyond Casterly Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.78,0:25:33.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个选择可能让你更好受些……\N{\fs40}One perhaps you might be more comfortable with, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.91,0:25:36.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,离家也更近些\N{\fs40}closer to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.66,0:25:38.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想的是谁？\N{\fs40}Who do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.00,0:25:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿王子\N{\fs40}Prince Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.51,0:25:54.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这孩子才刚刚两岁 奥托\N{\fs40}The boy just turned two, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.35,0:25:56.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 但这样就可以制止\N{\fs40}Yes, but it would cease
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.43,0:25:59.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那些络绎不绝向雷妮拉求婚的人了\N{\fs40}the endless proposals for Rhaenyra's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.77,0:26:03.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,-  给他们订下婚约……  - 我是来狩猎的\N{\fs40}- Betroth them... - I came here to hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.23,0:26:07.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是来被这堆该死的政治游戏逼到窒息的\N{\fs40}Not to be suffocated by all this fucking politicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.49,0:26:11.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就不提这个了\N{\fs40}Let us speak no more of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.00,0:27:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经派人去找雷妮拉了 陛下\N{\fs40}We've sent out riders to find Rhaenyra, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.84,0:27:09.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士跟着她呢\N{\fs40}Ser Criston went after her
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.17,0:27:10.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望他们正在一起\N{\fs40}so the hope is that they are together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.84,0:27:12.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这姑娘太叛逆了\N{\fs40}The girl is a heedless contrarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.51,0:27:17.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我反过来不准她嫁去兰尼斯特\N{\fs40}If I instead forbade her to wed a Lannister
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.22,0:27:20.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她一定会因为怨恨而跟杰森大人私奔\N{\fs40}she would have run off with Lord Jason out of spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.02,0:27:24.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我真是个了不起的坦格利安国王啊\N{\fs40}A truly great Targaryen king I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.44,0:27:28.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对自己十七岁的女儿感到无能为力\N{\fs40}Powerless over mine own daughter of seven-and-ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.61,0:27:32.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰赫里斯国王和平统治了半个世纪\N{\fs40}King Jaehaerys ruled over half a century of peace
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.45,0:27:35.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但孩子们快把他逼疯了\N{\fs40}while his children drove him to the edge of madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.91,0:27:37.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尤其是女儿\N{\fs40}His daughters in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.33,0:27:40.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是……传统 陛下\N{\fs40}It is... tradition, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,关于这件事 你想听听我的建议吗？\N{\fs40}Do you wish to hear my opinion on the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.55,0:27:55.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我猜一下？\N{\fs40}Should I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.47,0:28:02.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你认为你儿子 “碎骨人”哈尔温\N{\fs40}You believe that your son, Ser Harwin Breakbones
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.81,0:28:06.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七大王国最强壮的骑士\N{\fs40}the strongest knight in the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.15,0:28:08.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是雷妮拉最合适的人选\N{\fs40}is the best match for Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.02,0:28:12.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您抬举我了 陛下 但这不是我想说的\N{\fs40}You flatter me, Your Grace, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.19,0:28:15.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为最适合雷妮拉的人\N{\fs40}It would seem to me the best match for Rhaenyra
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.32,0:28:17.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是“海蛇”的儿子\N{\fs40}is the son of the Sea Snake
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.41,0:28:18.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.66,0:28:22.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,几年前 我建议你娶他姐姐为妻\N{\fs40}Some years ago, I counseled you to take his sister to wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.91,0:28:24.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如今理由依然相同\N{\fs40}My reasoning remains the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.96,0:28:29.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺有纯正的瓦雷利亚血统\N{\fs40}Laenor is of pure Valyrian descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.38,0:28:32.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他有您堂姐雷妮丝公主的血脉\N{\fs40}He shares blood with your cousin, the Princess Rhaenys
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:36.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是王国内最富有家族的继承人\N{\fs40}and he is the heir to the wealthiest house in the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.34,0:28:38.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您两家的的裂痕\N{\fs40}The breach between your houses
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.68,0:28:40.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自我上次提起 至今也未见愈合的迹象\N{\fs40}has not narrowed since I last spoke of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.51,0:28:42.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这样会大大减少外界对科利斯大人\N{\fs40}It would do much to assuage Lord Corlys
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.93,0:28:46.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或真或假的种种轻视\N{\fs40}of any slights, real or imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.48,0:28:52.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 我们得祈祷\N{\fs40}We must pray, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.90,0:28:55.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼诺能在石阶列岛战事中活下来\N{\fs40}that Laenor survives the fighting in the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.44,0:29:37.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主 我必须最后一次请求您返回营地\N{\fs40}Princess, I must make a final plea that we return to the camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.70,0:29:40.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我更想呆在这\N{\fs40}I rather prefer it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.74,0:29:45.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下一定非常担心您的缺席\N{\fs40}His Grace is certain to be worried by your absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.95,0:29:49.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下要这么爱担心那就担心死吧\N{\fs40}His Grace can worry himself to death if he so likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.26,0:30:01.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和我说说吧 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Tell me something, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.39,0:30:06.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你认为王国的臣民最终能接受我成为他们的女王吗？\N{\fs40}Do you think the realm will ever accept me as their Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.11,0:30:16.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,臣民除了接受别无选择 公主\N{\fs40}They'll have no choice but to, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.98,0:32:14.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您还好么 陛下？\N{\fs40}Is everything all right, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.81,0:32:19.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你也知道 我……\N{\fs40}You know, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.03,0:32:25.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我立她为王储是防止戴蒙荼毒王国\N{\fs40}I named her to protect the realm from Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.95,0:32:29.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那时她是我唯一的孩子\N{\fs40}She was my only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.24,0:32:32.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国之光\N{\fs40}The Realm's Delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.25,0:32:35.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我立她是出于爱……\N{\fs40}I named her out of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.38,0:32:39.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为我当时不再相信……\N{\fs40}because I no longer believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:42.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不再相信什么了 亲爱的？\N{\fs40}Believed what, my love?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.01,0:32:53.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的很多先祖都是驭龙者\N{\fs40}Many in my line have been dragonriders.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.10,0:32:58.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有极少数是梦行者\N{\fs40}Very few among us have been Dreamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.03,0:33:07.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙的力量跟预言的力量相比算什么？\N{\fs40}What is the power of a dragon next to the power of prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.66,0:33:10.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 时辰很晚了 夫君 - 雷妮拉很小的时候……\N{\fs40}- The hour is too late, husband. - When Rhaenyra was a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.29,0:33:13.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我做过一个梦\N{\fs40}I saw it in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.54,0:33:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我看到了 真切得像这篝火一样\N{\fs40}As vivid as these flames, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.54,0:33:22.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的妻子产下一名男婴\N{\fs40}A male babe, born to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.17,0:33:25.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,头戴征服者的王冠\N{\fs40}wearing the Conqueror's crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.55,0:33:29.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我太希望这梦能成真\N{\fs40}I so wanted it to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.39,0:33:32.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望自己也是个梦行者\N{\fs40}To be a Dreamer myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.68,0:33:37.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我企图重现那个梦 夜复一夜\N{\fs40}I sought that vision again, night after night
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.02,0:33:40.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但它再也没出现过\N{\fs40}but it never came again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.52,0:33:45.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我把心思和意念都倾注在它上面\N{\fs40}I poured all my thought and will into it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.32,0:33:51.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的魔怔最终害死了雷妮拉的母亲\N{\fs40}and my obsession killed Rhaenyra's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.49,0:33:52.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯\N{\fs40}Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.49,0:33:58.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我以为雷妮拉能带我走出悲伤和悔恨的深渊\N{\fs40}I thought Rhaenyra was the way out of my abyss of grief and regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.29,0:34:02.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把她立为继承人能让一切恢复如初\N{\fs40}That naming her heir would begin to set things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.84,0:34:05.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 一切都恢复了！ - 我没想过要续弦\N{\fs40}- Oh, it did! - I never imagined I would remarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.88,0:34:08.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没想过真能有个儿子\N{\fs40}That I would have a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.30,0:34:15.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,万一我错了呢？\N{\fs40}What if I was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.75,0:35:30.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 虽然不是白鹿 但也是个大家伙\N{\fs40}It may not be white, Your Grace, but he's a big lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.35,0:35:38.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.27,0:35:40.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请用它\N{\fs40}For the kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.38,0:36:07.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,往这刺 陛下\N{\fs40}Strike here, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.28,0:36:41.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 再来一次 往您的左手边一点\N{\fs40}One more time, Your Grace. A bit to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.88,0:38:14.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.25,0:39:40.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来吧 王子乖乖 让陛下消停一会\N{\fs40}Come, sweet prince. Let's give Her Grace some peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.69,0:39:57.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,殿下享受这次狩猎么？\N{\fs40}Did you enjoy the hunt, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.65,0:40:00.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还行吧\N{\fs40}Well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.61,0:40:02.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我外孙过得好吗？\N{\fs40}How fared my grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.24,0:40:05.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼斯特夫人和雷德温夫人可喜欢他了\N{\fs40}The ladies Lannister and Redwyne were quite taken with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.99,0:40:07.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,应该的\N{\fs40}As they should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.78,0:40:10.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是王国的未来\N{\fs40}He's the future of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.41,0:40:15.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你自己也看到这次庆典的规模了\N{\fs40}You yourself witnessed the scale of the celebration
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.58,0:40:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家多团结\N{\fs40}how it's united the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.09,0:40:19.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你给国王生下儿子时\N{\fs40}When you bore the King a son
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.42,0:40:22.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,十五年的疑虑都烟消云散了\N{\fs40}you ended 15 years of uncertainty and doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.51,0:40:28.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿 人如其名 生来就是要统治七国的\N{\fs40}Aegon, like his namesake, was born to rule the Seven Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.10,0:40:31.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果韦赛里斯把他立为王储 举国会为他欢庆\N{\fs40}If Viserys were to name him heir, the realm would fete him for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.11,0:40:39.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不欢喜么？\N{\fs40}Does this not please you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.36,0:40:42.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不希望儿子能当上国王么？\N{\fs40}Do you not want your son to be king?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.19,0:40:43.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哪个母亲不想啊？\N{\fs40}What mother wouldn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.86,0:40:46.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不能无视确凿的事实\N{\fs40}You mustn't ignore the certain truth
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.86,0:40:49.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果雷妮拉取代了伊耿称王\N{\fs40}that if Rhaenyra were to step over Aegon to ascend the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.03,0:40:52.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国就会分崩离析\N{\fs40}the realm would tear itself apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.41,0:40:57.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,各大家族已经向她宣誓效忠了 咱们家也一样\N{\fs40}They all swore obeisance to her, our house among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.67,0:40:59.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是伊耿出生之前\N{\fs40}That was before Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.88,0:41:02.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉会是个好女王\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra will be a good Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:06.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她就算是杰赫里斯再世也没用的\N{\fs40}It wouldn't matter if she were Jaehaerys himself born again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.84,0:41:10.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉是女人\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.60,0:41:11.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你把我儿子当什么？\N{\fs40}What of my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.93,0:41:14.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你想让我把他抚养成一个篡夺姐姐的天赐权利的人么？\N{\fs40}Would you have me raise a man to steal his own sister's birthright?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.81,0:41:17.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿才是被夺权的那个\N{\fs40}It is Aegon that's being robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.98,0:41:19.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他是国王的长子\N{\fs40}He's the firstborn son of the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.98,0:41:22.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,否认他对铁王座的继承权\N{\fs40}To deny that he is heir to the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.19,0:41:24.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就是蔑视诸神和世人的律法\N{\fs40}is to assail the laws of gods and men.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.74,0:41:30.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的前路并不确定 但结局很明确\N{\fs40}The road ahead is uncertain, but the end is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.78,0:41:32.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿会成为国王\N{\fs40}Aegon will be King.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.50,0:41:37.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要引导韦赛里斯恢复理智\N{\fs40}You must guide Viserys towards reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.00,0:41:42.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他自己想不明白的\N{\fs40}He'll never find it on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.76,0:41:51.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你还好么 夫君？\N{\fs40}How are you feeling, husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.55,0:41:54.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神在惩罚我过分享受了\N{\fs40}The gods have punished me for my indulgences.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.31,0:41:57.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 至少说明确实是好酒 - 好过头了\N{\fs40}- At least the wine was good. - Too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.57,0:42:12.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望咱们能讨论些事情\N{\fs40}I was hoping we might discuss something.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.74,0:42:16.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉的事么？\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.12,0:42:24.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得她不喜欢杰森·兰尼斯特作陪\N{\fs40}I do not think she enjoyed Jason Lannister's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.71,0:42:26.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,简直气死了\N{\fs40}She is cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.88,0:42:28.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我警告过你啦\N{\fs40}I warned you that she would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.01,0:42:31.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉到岁数了\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra has come of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.13,0:42:33.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她必须嫁给一位大领主 愿意敬她 护她\N{\fs40}She must needs marry a high lord who will honor her, defend her
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.93,0:42:35.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为王夫服侍她\N{\fs40}and serve her as king consort.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.35,0:42:39.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她想不想结婚根本不是重点\N{\fs40}Her wishes in this matter are irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.27,0:42:41.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信她会结婚的 陛下\N{\fs40}I do believe that Rhaenyra will marry, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.90,0:42:45.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但得让她相信那是她自己的选择\N{\fs40}But she must believe it is her choice to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.74,0:42:56.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 这是什么？ - 一封信\N{\fs40}- What's this? - A letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.29,0:43:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,魏蒙德·瓦列利安寄来的\N{\fs40}From Vaemond Velaryon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.46,0:43:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 海蛇的弟弟？ - 对\N{\fs40}- The Sea Snake's brother? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.96,0:43:09.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他和残余的部队还在石阶列岛作战\N{\fs40}He's fighting in the Stepstones with all the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.89,0:43:16.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能看看么？\N{\fs40}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.65,0:43:29.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科利斯大人和戴蒙王子快输了\N{\fs40}Lord Corlys and Prince Daemon are losing their war.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.90,0:43:32.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,据说战事非常不利\N{\fs40}Badly, by all accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.95,0:43:34.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是在请求援助\N{\fs40}This is a plea for aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.53,0:43:39.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那为何不援助呢？\N{\fs40}Then why not send it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.45,0:43:42.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为发动战争的是两个异见者\N{\fs40}Because it is a war started by two malcontents
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.71,0:43:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们对我的决策心怀不满\N{\fs40}unhappy with decisions I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.17,0:43:49.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我现在给戴蒙和科利斯提供援军\N{\fs40}If I now provide Daemon and Corlys succor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.50,0:43:51.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家会怎么看待我这个国王？\N{\fs40}what will that say of their King?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.13,0:43:53.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许会说国王是个好人 很爱自己的弟弟\N{\fs40}Perhaps that he is a good man who loves his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.84,0:43:56.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嗯 你要是真这么想 亲爱的\N{\fs40}Well, if you truly believe that, my dear
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.26,0:43:59.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只能说明你心胸宽广\N{\fs40}then you possess a generous spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.02,0:44:02.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你相信什么呢 韦赛里斯？\N{\fs40}What do you believe, Viserys?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.48,0:44:08.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得我就是个永远无法\N{\fs40}That I am forever doomed to anger one person
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.82,0:44:10.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,取悦所有人的倒霉蛋\N{\fs40}in the pleasing of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.28,0:44:13.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那我问个更简单的问题？\N{\fs40}Then I pose a simpler question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.28,0:44:17.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哪样更利于王国的稳定 是放任螃蟹喂食者壮大实力\N{\fs40}Is it better for the realm if the Crabfeeder thrives
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.37,0:44:18.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是把他斩草除根？\N{\fs40}or is vanquished?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.83,0:44:27.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,即刻动身前往矮石 亚当爵士\N{\fs40}Make haste to Dwarfstone, Ser Addam.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.88,0:44:30.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,务必亲手将它交给戴蒙王子\N{\fs40}Hand-deliver this to Prince Daemon yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.34,0:44:31.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,立刻去办 陛下\N{\fs40}At once, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.43,0:44:41.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,矮石？\N{\fs40}Dwarfstone?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.81,0:44:45.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我给戴蒙送去消息 援兵正驶往石阶列岛\N{\fs40}I'm sending word to Daemon. Aid is sailing to the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.35,0:44:50.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 他有要求增援吗？ - 他宁愿战死\N{\fs40}- Did he make call for help? - He would sooner die.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.19,0:44:53.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是他的国王不允许那样\N{\fs40}But his King does not mean to allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.03,0:45:00.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不觉得我的决定很正确吗？\N{\fs40}Do you not think my decision correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.33,0:45:04.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正如我经常被提醒的那样 这和我的想法并无关系\N{\fs40}It is no consequence to what I think, as I'm often reminded.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.37,0:45:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙就如深扎在我血肉里的刺\N{\fs40}Daemon is thorn enough in my flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.63,0:45:12.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你一定要学他吗？\N{\fs40}Will you insist on taking after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.92,0:45:15.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,每件事都必须争斗一番吗？\N{\fs40}Must everything be a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.88,0:45:19.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你指的是你想把我嫁到凯岩城……\N{\fs40}If you refer to your attempt to marry me off to Casterly Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.80,0:45:22.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}I am sorry, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.27,0:45:26.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我试着去帮你 你领情吗？\N{\fs40}I was trying to help you. Will you not be helped?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.10,0:45:32.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为什么在你身上的每一次努力都会遭到你的殊死抵抗？\N{\fs40}Why must every effort on your behalf be resisted as if to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.48,0:45:34.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为你想换掉我\N{\fs40}Because you mean to replace me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.40,0:45:40.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让阿莉森·海塔尔的儿子换掉我 他是你一直梦寐以求的男丁\N{\fs40}With Alicent Hightower's son. The boy you always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.91,0:45:44.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你现在已经拥他在手 我对你已经全然没有利用价值了\N{\fs40}You have him in hand now, you have no further use for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.37,0:45:47.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你大可以把我兜售个好价钱\N{\fs40}You might as well peddle me for what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.62,0:45:50.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,换一座山上的堡垒 一支庞大的舰队\N{\fs40}A mountain stronghold or a fleet of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.21,0:45:53.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你误解我了 雷妮拉\N{\fs40}You have misjudged me, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.42,0:45:55.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人尽皆知\N{\fs40}All know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.26,0:45:57.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰森·兰尼斯特知道这事\N{\fs40}Jason Lannister knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.42,0:45:58.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你亲口说的\N{\fs40}You said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.05,0:46:01.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全境的领主们像秃鹫一样聚集到我的尸体上\N{\fs40}The lords of the realm gather like vultures to a carcass
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.89,0:46:04.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想要饱餐一顿\N{\fs40}hoping to feast on my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.52,0:46:10.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为统治者我们确实需要为了利益来联姻\N{\fs40}It is true that as rulers we must marry for advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.81,0:46:13.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去建立联盟增强实力\N{\fs40}to forge alliances and bolster our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.86,0:46:16.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你也一直深谙这点\N{\fs40}You have always understood this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.15,0:46:19.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和你母亲订下婚事 那时才十……\N{\fs40}I myself was promised to your mother when I was ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.53,0:46:21.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,十七岁的年纪\N{\fs40}Ten-and-seven years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.53,0:46:23.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谷地有一支军队能与北境抗衡\N{\fs40}The Vale had an army to rival the North.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.45,0:46:25.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我记事起就一直听那个故事了\N{\fs40}I've heard that story since I've had ears to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:28.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我深爱她\N{\fs40}I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.83,0:46:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她让我成为了真正的男人\N{\fs40}She made a man of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.84,0:46:37.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想让其他人取代你 孩子\N{\fs40}I do not seek to replace you, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.84,0:46:41.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这几年你一直很孤独\N{\fs40}You've been much alone these last few years
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.09,0:46:43.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孤独又易怒\N{\fs40}alone and angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.64,0:46:46.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会长生不老\N{\fs40}I will not live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.47,0:46:49.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望看到你生活富足 幸福美满\N{\fs40}I wish to see you contented. Happy, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.06,0:46:52.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你觉得靠一个男人能办到？ - 是家庭\N{\fs40}- You think a man will do it? - A family.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.23,0:46:54.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我曾有过家庭 - 你想要我做什么？\N{\fs40}- I had a family. - What would you have me do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.07,0:46:58.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果真的是为了利益考虑 你当初就该迎娶兰娜尔·瓦列利安！\N{\fs40}If it was for advantage, you would have wed Laena Velaryon!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.12,0:47:04.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说的没错\N{\fs40}That is true enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.49,0:47:09.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你必须结婚\N{\fs40}You must marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.25,0:47:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,加强你的继承人地位\N{\fs40}Strengthen your own claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.92,0:47:16.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,巩固你的继承权 赶紧生孩子\N{\fs40}Shore up your succession. Multiply.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.09,0:47:19.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至于你的良配……\N{\fs40}As to your match...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.42,0:47:22.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你自己选\N{\fs40}make it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.97,0:47:25.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,找到他\N{\fs40}Search him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.89,0:47:27.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,找一个你喜欢的\N{\fs40}Find one that pleases you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.01,0:47:29.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就像我那样\N{\fs40}As I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.99,0:47:46.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.12,0:47:53.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的确动摇过\N{\fs40}I did waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.12,0:47:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有那么一阵\N{\fs40}At one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.63,0:48:00.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我现在以你母亲的名义向你发誓\N{\fs40}But I swear to you now, on your mother's memory
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.13,0:48:03.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不会被取代\N{\fs40}you will not be supplanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.64,0:48:49.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们有16艘 或许18艘适航的船只\N{\fs40}We have 16, perhaps 18, seaworthy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.85,0:48:52.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,700名步兵 约60名骑士\N{\fs40}700 foot, some 60 knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.22,0:48:53.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,粮草消耗很快\N{\fs40}Our food quickly dwindles
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.60,0:48:55.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽管能从海中补充些渔获\N{\fs40}save for what we can fish from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.14,0:48:57.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想还能坚持两周\N{\fs40}I would say we have a fortnight
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.81,0:48:59.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许在严格的配给管理下能再久些\N{\fs40}mayhaps a bit longer with strict rationing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.36,0:49:02.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已经求助潮头岛派更多的船\N{\fs40}I've made call for Driftmark to send more ships
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.73,0:49:04.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但还要几周才能到\N{\fs40}but they will be weeks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.03,0:49:07.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我军的势头正在衰弱 三城同盟会知道这点\N{\fs40}We are faltering and the Triarchy knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.74,0:49:11.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们必须加紧进攻 继续派出龙\N{\fs40}We must press the attack. Continue sending the dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.58,0:49:12.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是徒劳的 父亲\N{\fs40}It's pointless, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.79,0:49:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,螃蟹喂食者把住了咽喉要道\N{\fs40}The Crabfeeder's created a chokepoint here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.50,0:49:18.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就在这些沙丘后方\N{\fs40}beyond these dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.83,0:49:21.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,弓箭手占据高地 步兵占据平地\N{\fs40}Archers hold the high positions, foot soldiers hold the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.05,0:49:24.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们一次又一次地在龙背上扫射\N{\fs40}We strafe them on dragonback again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.13,0:49:25.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他们只是撤退到洞穴里\N{\fs40}but they just retreat within the caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.63,0:49:30.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙们可以在血石上盘旋 直到它们从天上下来\N{\fs40}Dragons can circle Bloodstone until they fall out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.72,0:49:33.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,螃蟹喂食者和他的人没有理由离开洞穴\N{\fs40}The Crabfeeder and his men have no reason to leave those caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.89,0:49:35.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们必须给他们一个理由\N{\fs40}We must give them one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.60,0:49:37.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一块引诱螃蟹的肉\N{\fs40}An offering of flesh to bait the crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.60,0:49:39.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谁？\N{\fs40}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.15,0:49:41.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙回来了！\N{\fs40}Dragon returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.36,0:49:50.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没错 谁？\N{\fs40}Yes, who?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.82,0:49:53.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这里有谁愿意欣然赴死？\N{\fs40}Which man here will happily go to his death?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.33,0:49:55.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,侄儿 让我看看哪个骑士会慷慨下地狱？\N{\fs40}Show me the knight who will march into that hellpit
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.41,0:49:57.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我让你看看疯子是什么样子\N{\fs40}nephew, and I will show you a madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.29,0:50:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 戴蒙 - 戴蒙是我们失败的原因\N{\fs40}- Daemon. - Daemon is why we are losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.13,0:50:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他至少还在打仗\N{\fs40}He at least is fighting this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.54,0:50:05.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,叔叔 你在这个议会中扮演了什么角色？\N{\fs40}What role have you played in this council, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.13,0:50:07.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 除了当抱怨大臣 还有吗？ - 够了 兰尼诺\N{\fs40}- Other than master of complaints? - Enough, Laenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.47,0:50:10.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果君临不支援戴蒙\N{\fs40}If King's Landing will not support Daemon
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.26,0:50:11.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要这样做？\N{\fs40}why should any of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.10,0:50:22.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,管你是不是我的血亲 魏蒙德 我不会让你煽动叛乱\N{\fs40}Blood or no, Vaemond, I will not have you stoke mutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.84,0:50:46.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你不尽力去掌控这场战争 大人\N{\fs40}If you do not seize control of this war, my lord
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.30,0:50:48.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们所有人早晚会葬身蟹腹\N{\fs40}the crabs will soon dine on all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.07,0:51:06.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙王子\N{\fs40}Prince Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.69,0:51:10.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我带来了韦塞里斯·坦格利安一世陛下\N{\fs40}I bring word from His Grace, Viserys Targaryen First of His Name,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.35,0:51:13.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安达尔人 洛伊拿人和先民的国王\N{\fs40}King of the Andals, the Rhoynar and the First Men
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.24,0:51:15.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七国统治者暨全境守护者的旨意\N{\fs40}Lord of the Seven Kingdoms, and Protector of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.49,0:52:00.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,够了！\N{\fs40}That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.75,0:52:02.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,停下！\N{\fs40}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.85,0:52:18.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,弟弟……\N{\fs40}Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.93,0:52:21.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已下令派出十艘船\N{\fs40}I have ordered ten ships
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.31,0:52:24.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及2000兵力 即刻从君临出发\N{\fs40}and 2,000 men to set sail from King's Landing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.39,0:52:26.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为石阶列岛的战斗出力\N{\fs40}to join the effort in the Stepstones.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.23,0:52:31.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽管机缘使我们彼此疏远\N{\fs40}Though time and circumstance have seen us estranged
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.82,0:52:35.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要知道 我不希望看到你的行动失败\N{\fs40}know that it is not my desire to see you fail in your course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.45,0:52:39.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,相反 我希望这次援助将带来\N{\fs40}It is instead my hope that this aid will deliver the victory
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.74,0:52:41.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,迄今为止我们未能取得的胜利\N{\fs40}that has thus far evaded us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.16,0:52:47.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我将每晚向诸神祈祷你平安归来\N{\fs40}I shall pray nightly to the gods for your safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.28,0:54:42.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,搭箭\N{\fs40}Nock.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.18,0:55:08.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拉弓\N{\fs40}Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.43,0:55:49.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放箭！\N{\fs40}Loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.44,0:55:58.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放箭！\N{\fs40}Loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.62,0:56:15.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放箭！\N{\fs40}Loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.27,0:56:35.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放箭！\N{\fs40}Loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.22,0:59:18.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰！\N{\fs40}Dracarys!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.24,0:59:33.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,搭箭！\N{\fs40}Nock!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.70,0:59:35.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙来了！\N{\fs40}Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.07,1:00:57.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰！\N{\fs40}Dracarys!
